  "text": "On In-shop Clothes we report R@K for value of K ∈ {1, 10, 20, 30, 50} in Tab. 4. The best-performing method is probably FastAP, even though the situation regarding reproducibility is rather puzzling 3 . RaMBO matches the performance of ABE-8 [CITATION_1] , a complex attention-based ensemble method.",
